creating  a simple Quora application

to create, edit, read , delete posts

steps:
npm init -y
npm i express
npm i ejs
create file index.js aquire express and set up the server
create folders views and public
create file views/index.ejs with html code . render this page in the index.js file i.e server side code
create file views/post.ejs with html code to create a post(that s create post form) and soo on

npm i uuid -> (Universally unique identifier) this is for generating unique id for each posts